casuarina: Use libhidlbase_shim instead of libhidlbase-v32 for vendor.fpsensor.hardware.fpsensorhidlsvc@2.0.so

Using libhidlbase-v32 just straight up crashing the library and cause null
pointer dereference in Lineage fingerprint AIDL HAL. On the other side,
libhidlbase_shim doesn't do that, and yet still provides the shim we wanted.
